title: Kesaksian Keluarga, Eril Sempat Berteriak HELP
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Perwakilan keluarga Gubernur Jawa Barat Elpi Nazmuzzaman menceritakan detik-detik Emmeril terbawa arus sempat berteriak minta tolong. ||||"Mungkin karena ponakan kami ini pemuda yang bertanggung jawab, menjaga kelompok, ibunya tidak ikut turun, beliau memastikan yang punya skill cukup yang turun begitu situasinya. Saat kejadian info dari keluarga memastikan 2 sudah sampai, lalu terjadi terbawa arus Eril berteriak help,"ucap Perwakilan keluarga Gubernur Jawa Barat Elpi Nazmuzzaman.||||Teriakan Erik terdengar oleh warga setempat dan menelepon kepolisian setempat. ||||Baca Juga Drone Pendeteksi Suhu Panas Tubuh Hingga Penyelam Dikerahkan Dalam Pencarian Emmeril di Swiss di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293382/drone-pendeteksi-suhu-panas-tubuh-hingga-penyelam-dikerahkan-dalam-pencarian-emmeril-di-swiss||||"Keluarga mendengar teriakan help terdengar warga di pinggiran sungai dan menelepon polisi. Keluarga ketemu polisi dan polisi sigap untuk memantau wisatawan,"jelas Elpi. ||||Tim SAR dan Polisi Swiss serta tim penyelam dikerahkan untuk mencari Emmeril hingga Sabtu (28/5/2022). ||||Keluarga, kerabat dari Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil berharap yang terbaik dalam upaya pencarian tersebut. ||||Video Editor: Galih|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293386/kesaksian-keluarga-eril-sempat-berteriak-help

title: â€˜Poland nextâ€¦â€™: Putin ally's threat sends shivers in Europe; Ramzan Kadyrov warns on arming Ukraine
description: Chechen leader Ramzan Kadyrov, who is a staunch ally of Russian President Vladimir Putin, has now threatened to target Poland after Ukraine. An undated video of Kadyrov is going viral, where he can be heard saying that the issue of Ukraine is closed, and if given the order, he's interested in Poland. He warned the NATO member "to better take back your weapons from Ukraine as he is ready to attack the European country." Poland is one of the countries that has supplied weapons to Ukraine to defend itself from Russia's invasion. The Polish government says it has supplied weapons worth $1.6 billion, including hundreds of tanks, howitzers, and Grad rocket launchers to Ukraine. Watch this video for more details.|#Poland #ChechenLeader #RamzanKadyrov #Russia #Chechnya #Ukraine #War #Invasion #NATO #Europe #ValdimirPutin #RussianPresident

title: Putin's war next door, ex-Soviet satellite state Romania orders grounded MiG-21s back into air
description: Romania will be using MiG-21s for one more year, just a month after deciding to ground the Soviet-era jets. Romania shares a border with Ukraine; NATO has sent troop reinforcements & equipment to the ex-Soviet satellite state. Maintaining a high-alert status critical for Romania, the MiG-21s will be used for air policing & flight training. title: Toyota GR86 2022 | E giÃ  SOLD OUT. PerchÃ¨ Ã¨ DIVERTENTISSIMA
description: La nuova Toyota GR86 Ã¨ finalmente realtÃ . Dopo la prima presa di contatto di qualche mese fa su un prototipo, oggi riusciamo finalmente a mettere mano sulla versione definitiva, scoprendo che tutto quello che avevamo apprezzato su quella macchina camuffata si ritrova anche nel prodotto di serie. E questo Ã¨ veramente positivo perchÃ© se da un lato viene da chiedersi come quegli elementi analogici possano essere ancora attuali in un panorama automobilistico sempre piÃ¹ elettrico-digitale, dall'altro dimostrano come in alcune nicchie di mercato vi siano ancora migliaia di persone disposte ad acquistare prodotti analogici e che sappiano emozionare. Del resto anche oggi che il CD Ã¨ superato...continuano ad essere venduti giradischi e vinili, con grande gioia degli amanti del genere. Anzi, quel fenomeno ha scatenato una parabola positiva che ha riportato moltissimi sui propri passi.|Questo non significa che la GR86 fermerÃ  la digitalizzazione dell'auto, anzi da metÃ  2024 non sarÃ  piÃ¹ nemmeno commercializzata in Europa per via dell'arrivo della normativa Euro7 alla quale questo progetto "non aderirÃ " ufficialmente, ma in quest'ultima boccata di ossigeno automobilistico Ã¨ bello apprezzare come gli sforzi dell'accoppiata Toyota Subaru per allargare la proposta in ambito sportivo siano orientati in una giusta direzione e facciano parte di un programma, almeno in casa Toyota, che attraverso i suoi successi nel racing ed i suoi prodotti ha portato risultati anche nelle vendite dei prodotti normali.|257 cm di passo, 426 cm di lunghezza, la Toyota GR86 Ã¨ un progetto che parte dalle basi progettuali della GT86 andando perÃ² a migliorarne gli aspetti che ne limitavano le qualitÃ  dinamiche: a fronte di un telaio pazzesco e di una qualitÃ  di guida sopraffina, infatti, la precedente edizione di questa moderna erede della AE86 era carente di motore e cosÃ¬ dal precedente boxer 1.998 cc si Ã¨ passati ad un piÃ¹ prestazionale 2.387 cc (alesaggio 94 mm e corsa 86 mm) che gira fino a 7.500 giri offrendo 234 CV e 250 Nm di coppia massima a 3.700 giri contro i precedenti 205 a 6.400. Niente di sconvolgente, in realtÃ , anche perchÃ© lo 0-100 km/h viene coperto in 6,3 secondi contro i 7,6 precedenti ma quanto basta per stravolgere il comportamento della vettura, in particolar modo alle basse ed alle medie velocitÃ  dove la posizione bassa del baricentro (motore boxer), l'assetto, gli irrigidimenti della scocca messi a punto per questo nuovo modello ed il differenziale autobloccante Torsen, consentono di avere un filo diretto con le ruote posteriori attivando una sorta di secondo asse sterzante comandato con il...pedale del gas. Il tutto coadiuvato, naturalmente da uno schema sospensioni McPherson davanti e doppio braccio al posteriore.|Spartana, come sempre, la GR86 Ã¨ dotata di un sistema multimediale "base" ma con apple carplay ed android auto...ed a livello di interni non ha nulla di eccezionale se non la grande semplicitÃ  che la contraddistingue da sempre e che la fa pesare il giusto: 1.264 kg, infatti, sono un valore di tutto rispetto a fronte di valori di sicurezza passiva su cui Toyota e Subaru sono state intransigenti.|2+2 con un bagagliaio da 276 litri - peccato solo per la mancanza del portellone - la nuova GR86 viene proposta sul mercato italiano in due varianti di allestimento: Sport e Sport Premium. In realtÃ  sono due differenti tipologie di prodotto perchÃ© se Ã¨ vero che la Sport Ã¨ un po' meno ricca sotto il profilo di allestimento va anche detto che le ruote da 17" sono piÃ¹ inclini ad offrire un comportamento dinamico piÃ¹ "driftoso", soprattutto alle basse velocitÃ . Ovvero laddove con le 18" gommate Pilot Super Sport c'Ã¨ ancora molto grip. Personalmente le avrei chiamarte Drift, la base, e Sport la variante con i 18...che onestamente sfrutta molto meglio il nuovo motore ed il telaio aggiornato in chiave tempo sul giro. C'Ã¨ anche una versione automatica, con cambio Aisin a convertitore di coppia e sei marce: porta con se anche gli adas di livello 2, che aggiungono il cruise control adattivo ed il mantenimento della carreggiata ai giÃ  presenti sistemi antitamponamento, ma onestamente in una macchina del genere il cambio automatico mi sembra fuori luogo.|Prezzi? 34.250 euro la Sport, 36.750 euro la Sport Premium. |Vi lascio alla mia prova su strada test drive. Ciao Emiliano Perucca Orfei Masterpilot

title: BREAKING NEWS - Update KBRI Bern Soal Emmeril Anak Ridwan Kamil yang Terseret Arus Sungai di Swiss
description: KOMPAS.TV - Pihak keluarga Ridwan Kamil masih menantikan kabar terkait pencarian Emmeril Khan Mumtadz, putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil.|Eril diinformasikan hilang terseret arus Sungai Aare di Bern, Swiss dan belum ditemukan hingga kini.|Pencarian terhadap Eril sudah dilakukan tanggal 26 Mei 2022 di Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss.|Keluarga meminta dukungan doa untuk pencarian Eril.|Anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril hilang saat tengah berenang di Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss, Kamis 26 Mei.|Saat itu Eril tengah berenang di Sungai Aare bersama adik dan kawannya.|Namun ketikan akan naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras.|Sementara itu, Duta Besar RI untuk Swiss, Muliaman Hadad seperti yang kami kutip dari Kompas.com menyatakan, pencarian akan kembali dilakukan hari ini.|Pihak polisi dan SAR akan melanjutkan pencarian.|Saat kejadian, ayah Emmeril, Ridwan Kamil berada di Inggris bersama delegasi Pemprov Jawa Barat.|Dalam unggahan di media sosial instagramnya, RK memperlihatkan aktivitasnya membahas kerjasama join campus dengan University Of Lancaster dan investasi bidang energi terbarukan.|Mendengar kabar putranya hilang, RK pun langsung menyusul ke Swiss.|Sahabat KompasTV, jangan lupa like, comment, dan subscribe channel YouTube KompasTV, juga aktifkan lonceng notifikasi agar tidak ketinggalan update mengenai isu-isu terkini di Indonesia.|Jangan lewatkan live streaming KompasTV 24 jam non stop di https://www.kompas.tv/live. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.|About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:|--------------------------------------------------------------------|The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. title: Life below the war torn streets of Kharkiv - BBC News
description: "My tears say it all. It's very hard. Why do we have to suffer?"|Zhenia is one of many people living in the metro tunnels beneath the war torn city of Kharkiv in northeast Ukraine.|She has been wearing the same clothes since her home was hit by Russian artillery in February, forcing her to seek refuge in the station with many others from similar situations.|But the longer they remain in the station without fresh air or the ability to wash, the more people are getting ill.|This is life below the war torn streets of Kharkiv.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Russia #Ukraine #BBCNews

title: THE ULTIMATE REMATCH | MSI 2022 - Semifinals Day 2 Tease
description: This is the end of a semifinal trilogy that spans back to 2019 when G2 Esports defeated T1 at both MSI and Worlds semifinals. Before Caps joined G2, Faker and T1 saw a clear superiority over G2 Esports. Since then though, the rivalry has swung in the favor of G2. Caps and G2 are 9-4 against the South Korean champions. One of Fakerâ€™s worst losses of all time came in the 2019 Worlds final when he fell apart against G2 in front of the European fans in Madrid. Can Faker and T1 gain some revenge and take them down in front of their hometown fans in Busan, South Korea?|This is a match Faker has been waiting for for three years. title: Hsiung-Feng II, Sky Bow III: Taiwan flaunts missile firepower as Beijing flexes military muscle
description: In a strong message to China, Taiwan conducted military exercises and displayed its missile power. Taiwan's air, sea and land forces, including the coast guard, held a joint missile firing exercise. Taiwan's exercises come close on heels of Beijing conducting military drills near the island. Taiwan flaunted several missiles during the drill including MBDA MICA, Hsiung-Feng II & Sky Bow III. The navy fired the RIM-66 standard missile from the Cheng Kung class frigate warship. The footage showed Taiwanâ€™s air force firing a MBDA MICA missile from a mirage jet. Watch the full video for more.|#Taiwan #China #Hsiung-FengII #SkyBowIII

title: PM Modi visits Matushri K.D.P. Multi-speciality Hospital in Atkot, Gujarat
description: Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi will visit Gujarat on 28 May, 2022. At around 10:30 AM, Prime Minister will visit the newly built Matushri K.D.P. Multispeciality Hospital in Atkot, Rajkot. This will be followed by his address at a public function at the venue. Thereafter, at around 4 PM, Prime Minister will address the Seminar of leaders of various cooperative institutions on 'Sahakar Se Samriddhi' at Mahatma Mandir, Gandhinagar, where he will also inaugurate the Nano Urea (Liquid) Plant constructed at IFFCO, Kalol.|PM in Gandhinagar|The cooperative sector of Gujarat has been a role model for the entire nation. There are more than 84,000 societies in the State in the Cooperative Sector. About 231 lakh members are associated with these societies. In yet another step towards further strengthening the cooperative movement in the state, the organization of a Seminar of leaders of various Cooperative institutions on 'Sahakar Se Samriddhi' will take place at Mahatma Mandir, Gandhinagar. More than 7,000 representatives from various cooperative institutions of the State will participate in the Seminar.|In an effort to further provide farmers the means to boost productivity and help increase their income, Prime Minister will also inaugurate the Nano Urea (Liquid) Plant constructed at IFFCO, Kalol at a cost of around Rs. 175 crores. The ultramodern Nano Fertilizer Plant has been established keeping in mind the increase in crop yield through the use of Nano Urea. The Plant will produce about 1.5 lakh bottles of 500 ml per day.|PM in Atkot, Rajkot|Matushri K.D.P. Multispeciality Hospital, which is being visited by the Prime Minister, is managed by Shree Patel Seva Samaj. It will make available high end medical equipment and provide world class healthcare facilities to the people of the region. The visit will be followed by Prime Ministerâ€™s address at a public function.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! ğŸ””||||Follow us to stay updated:||||â–º Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||â–º Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi

title: Begini Kondisi Cuaca saat Emmeril Anak Ridwan Kamil Terseret Arus di Sungai Aaree Swiss
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Adik Ridwan Kamil, Elpi Nazmuzaman menyampaikan musibah yang menimpa Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz bermula saat Eril dan teman-temannya mandi di sungai.||||Dalam keterangannya, kondisi cuaca saat kejadian dalam kondisi cuaca cerah.||||"Saat ingin naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras yang sebelumnya sempat mendapat bantuan dari kawannya. Kejadian tersebut terjadi pada tanggal 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss dengan kondisi cuaca cerah,"ujar Elpi dalam keterangan resminya.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Anak Ridwan Kamil Diduga Terseret Arus Saat Berenang di Sungai Aaree Swiss di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293083/kronologi-anak-ridwan-kamil-diduga-terseret-arus-saat-berenang-di-sungai-aaree-swiss||||Hingga Sabtu (28/5) Waktu Indonesia, Tim SAR dan Polisi Swiss masih terus melakukan pencarian.||||Keluarga memohon doa agar Eril dapat segera ditemukan dalam keadaan selamat dan baik.||||Video Editor: Ian Andrian||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293320/begini-kondisi-cuaca-saat-emmeril-anak-ridwan-kamil-terseret-arus-di-sungai-aaree-swiss

title: CHICKEN TIKKA HANDI RECIPE | CHICKEN TIKKA HANDI RESTAURANT STYLE
description: Chicken Tikka Handi Recipe | Chicken Tikka Handi Restaurant Style | Chicken Tikka Masala Handi | Restaurant Style Chicken Handi | Chicken Handi Recipe | Chicken Handi by Spice Eats | Boneless Chicken Gravy | Chicken Recipe| Boneless Chicken Curry Recipe|Ingredients for Chicken Tikka Handi:|(Tsp- Teaspoon; Tbsp- Tablespoon )|Boneless Chicken - 500 gms|For Marination:|- Salt- 1 tsp|- Turmeric powder- 1/4 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 1.5 tsp |Tempering:-|- Cumin seeds - 1 tsp|- Whole red Chillies- 4|- Lightly crushed:|- Green Cardamoms- 5|- Cloves- 5|- Cinnamon- 2 |Spice Powders:|- Turmeric Powder- 1/4 tsp|- Red Chilli Powder- 1.5 tsp|- Kashmiri Chilli Powder- 1 tsp|- Coriander Powder- 2 tsp|- Cumin Powder- 1/2 tsp|- Later:|- Garam Masala Powder- 1/2 tsp |- Kasuri Methi Powder- 1 tsp |Other Ingredients:|- Grated Onion- 150 gms (2 medium)|- Ginger crushed- 1.5 tsp |- Garlic, crushed - 1.5 tsp (6 cloves)-15 gms|- Gram Flour (Besan) - 1.25 Tbsp (can also use chickpea flour)|- Tomato PurÃ©e - 5 tbsp|- Green Chillies, sliced - 3 |- Fresh cream - 4-5 tbsp|- Salt- 1/2 tsp + 1/4 tsp seasoning|Preparation: |- Take boneless breast and thigh pieces and cut these into bite sized pieces.  |- Now add the items for the marinade, give a mix and set aside for 30 mins. |- Grate the onions. You can use a grater or roughly pulse cubed onions in a grinder/blender to get the roughly grated onions. Do not make into a paste. |- Roughly crush the whole garam masalas in a mortar & pestle. Set aside. ( if you donâ€™t like crushed garam masala you can also add whole but there could be variation in flavour. )|- Peel and crush the ginger and garlic in a mortar & pestle. Set aside.|- Slice the green chillies. |- For the Kasuri Methi, dry roast it on low heat for around 30 secs and set aside to cool. Now crush it with your hand and set aside.|Process: |- To fry the chicken pieces, heat 1 tbsp oil in a pan and add the marinated chicken pieces. Fry on high to medium heat for 5 mins till browned. Switch off heat and set aside. |- Heat 3 tbsp oil in a kadhai or pan, add the cumin seeds, the crushed whole garam masalas and the whole red chillies. Mix and stir for 30 secs. |- Now add the grated onion, give a mix and add 1/2 tsp salt,|- Fry on medium to low heat for 4-5 mins.|- Add the crushed ginger & garlic and fry on medium to low heat for 2-3 mins. |- Now add gram flour(besan)/chickpea flour, mix and cook on low heat for 2 mins. |- Also add the spice powders and 100 ml water. Mix and fry on low heat for 3-4 mins till oil separates. |- Add tomato purÃ©e & 50 ml water, mix and fry for 3-4 mins on medium to low heat till oil separates. |- Add the fried chicken pieces, give a mix and fry for 2-3 mins on medium heat.|- And sliced green Chillies and fry for 1-2 mins on low heat.|- Next add 250 ml water, give a mix and cover & cook on low heat for 12 mins till meat is tender. |- Add the garam masala powder, dry roasted and powdered Kasuri Methi, pinch of salt and fresh cream. Give a mix. |- You can also add around 50 ml water, based on desired consistency, mix and cook for 3 mins on low heat.|- Serve with roti, naan or rice.|#chickentikkahandi #chickenhandirecipe #chickentikkamasalahandi #chickenrecipe #bonelesschickengravy #chickengravy #chickencurry #spiceeats #spiceeatsrecipes #spiceeatschicken

title: University Hospital trauma team recounts what they saw treating victims after Uvalde elementary ...
description: The trauma team from San Antonio's University Hospital waited almost two hours for the first patient from the school shooting to arrive from Robb Elementary School in Uvalde on Tuesday. KSAT anchor Steve Spriester got a behind-the-scenes tour with the trauma specialists as they recounted what happened that day and when they finally realized that the patients they'd prepared for were never coming.

title: Volunteers work to create custom caskets for victims of Uvalde school shooting
description: Volunteers are working nonstop in Edna, Texas, to deliver custom caskets to the families of the victims of the Robb Elementary mass shooting in Uvalde. So far, 17 families have taken up the offer. The first six caskets were driven overnight from Georgia, and staff members are working on painting and designing them. They will be delivered to Uvalde on Saturday.

title: Joy Reid Slams Cruz NRA Speech: Do Texans Want To Send Their Kids To Schools That Look Like Prison?

title: Japanese missiles and jets in India soon; New Delhi, Tokyo sign key pact on military cooperation
description: Japan plans to allow the exports of lethal military equipment, including missiles and jets, to India and 11 other countries, a move that could bolster efforts by New Delhi and Tokyo to cooperate in defence manufacturing. The development comes days after Prime Minister Narendra Modi and his Japanese counterpart Fumio Kishida agreed to enhance bilateral security and defence cooperation, including in defence manufacturing, during a meeting on the margins of the Quad Leaders Summit in Tokyo on Tuesday. title: Scottie Scheffler shoots 6-under 64 | Round 2 | Charles Schwab | 2022
description: In the second round of the 2022 Charles Schwab Challenge, Scottie Scheffler carded a 6-under 64 to get to 9-under for the tournament, placing him in a three-way tie for the lead with Beau Hossler and Scott Stallings heading into the weekend.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Five of the top 10 players in the world will tee it up this week at Colonial Country Club in Fort Worth, Texas, for the Charles Schwab Challenge. After missing his first cut since October 2021 at last weekâ€™s PGA Championship, World No.1 Scottie Scheffler will be hoping for a return to the incredible form that has seen him win four times already this season. Defending champion Jason Kokrak will make his return to Texas, as will RBC Heritage winner Jordan Spieth, who narrowly missed out on a victory last year, after shooting 73 in the final round. Fresh from his record-equaling comeback victory at the PGA Championship, Justin Thomas will be full of confidence in Fort Worth, however, heâ€™ll have to significantly improve upon his 2021 performance, which saw him finish 12 shots off the lead in T43, if he is going to taste victory for a second week in a row.||||||Welcome to the official YouTube channel of the PGA TOUR. Here you can find everything you need to stay up to date with the worldâ€™s foremost golf tour. Continue the journey on Digital May 31st. https://www.sonypictures.com/movies/fatherstu|Follow Us on Social:|https://www.facebook.com/FatherStuMovie|https://www.instagram.com/FatherStuMovie|https://www.twitter.com/FatherStuMovie| |Subscribe to the Sony Pictures YouTube Channel for more exclusive content: |http://bit.ly/SonyPicsSubscribe| |Based on a true story, Father Stu is an unflinchingly honest, funny and ultimately uplifting drama about a lost soul who finds his purpose in a most unexpected place. When an injury ends his amateur boxing career, Stuart Long (Mark Wahlberg) moves to L.A. dreaming of stardom. While scraping by as a supermarket clerk, he meets Carmen (Teresa Ruiz), a Catholic Sunday school teacher who seems immune to his bad-boy charm. Determined to win her over, the longtime agnostic starts going to church to impress her. But surviving a terrible motorcycle accident leaves him wondering if he can use his second chance to help others find their way, leading to the surprising realization that he is meant to be a Catholic priest. Despite a devastating health crisis and the skepticism of Church officials and his estranged parents (Mel Gibson and Jacki Weaver), Stu pursues his vocation with courage and compassion, inspiring not only those closest to him but countless others along the way.| |Written for the screen and directed by Rosalind Ross, and starring Academy Award NomineeÂ® Mark Wahlberg (Best Supporting Actor, The Departed, 2006) as Father Stu, along with Academy Award WinnerÂ® Mel Gibson (Best Director, Braveheart, 1995), Academy Award NomineeÂ® Jacki Weaver (Best Supporting Actor, Silver Linings Playbook, 2012) and Teresa Ruiz (Narcos). title: PlayStation State Of Play Announced Ahead of Summer Games Fest | GameSpot News
description: Sony announced a new PlayStation State of Play and revealed two new TV shows, Mario Strikers: Battle League gets an online demo and Nintendo Switch Online gets 3 new classic games.|#GamingNews #PlayStation #StateofPlay|Sony has announced a new PlayStation State of Play airing next week, promising new announcements including games for the PSVR2. The event, which is said to run for roughly 30 minutes, will take place on Thursday, June 2 at 3 PM PT / 6 PM ET and we will be streaming it right here on the GameSpot YouTube channel.|In other Sony news, the company announced two new TV shows during an earnings presentation Q&A. The shows include, a God of War TV series is coming to Amazon and a Horizon series is being made for Netflix.|In Nintendo news, a Switch demo for Mario Strikers: Battle League online mode will go live from June 3 and until June 5. Anyone with a Nintendo Switch Online membership can access the demo, and the tutorial section of the game is now live--for Expansion Pass members--so that you can get some practice time in.|STAMPS|00:00 - Intro|00:05 - PlayStation State of Play|01:26 - PlayStation TV Shows|01:54 - Mario Strikers Demo|02:18 - New NES & SNES Games

title: Federal Government Uses Defense Production Act For The Third Time This Week

title: Texas DPS Director Admits Police Were Slow To Act During Uvalde School Shooting
description: Texas Department of Public Safety Director Steven McCraw admitted police on the scene at Robb Elementary School were too slow to act and should have stormed the classroom sooner. Officials say as many as 19 officers were in a hallway by 12:03 pm but the door to the 4th grade classroom, with the shooter inside, was not breached until 47 minutes later using the janitorâ€™s key. title: OBI-WAN KENOBI Ep2: Every EASTER EGG and Full BREAKDOWN
description: Thanks to Established Titles for sponsoring this video! To take advantage of their Memorial Day sale right now, go to http://establishedtitles.com/Screencrush and use the discount code 'Screencrush' for an additional 10% off on all purchases and help support the channel.|Obi-Wan Kenobi episode sets the table for the rest of the Star Wars series. Obi-Wan rescues Leia, but learns the awful truth that Anakin is now Darth Vader. In this video we break down every Star wars easter Egg and connection to the prequels and the original trilogy.|If you're new, Subscribe! â†’ http://bit.ly/subscribe-screencrush|Go here â†’ http://screencrush.com/|Like us â†’ https://www.facebook.com/ScreenCrush|Follow us â†’ https://twitter.com/screencrushnews|Get our newsletter â†’ http://screencrush.com/newsletter/|Written and Hosted by Ryan Arey (http://twitter.com/ryanarey)|Edited by Harriet Lengel-Enright, Randolf Nombrado, Sean Martin and Srinidhi Rao|Research by Srinidhi Rao|The episode begins on a transport ship to Daiyu, an anything goes planet where they deliberately block the wifi [we block the signals] what happens on daiyu, stays on daiyu. ScrreenCrush matt Singer pointed out that the design of Daiyu seems lifted from the concept art of Star Wars Underworlds, the live action TV series set on Coruscant that was never produced. |There are a lot of Aurebesh letters in this episode which I am going to translate for you a little bit later on. Be patient, itâ€™s taking us a while.|Hey everyone, look, itâ€™s Temura Morrison returning as a clone trooper begging for money. His aging is accelerated, meaning by the time the empire is overthrown, heâ€™ll be an old man, like Rex.|Obi wan stares at him for a while, not just because heâ€™s a reminder of the clone wars and orders 66â€“but this guy is weaning armor from the 501st. Thatâ€™s the stormtrooper regiment attached to Anakin that killed younglings in the Jedi temple. |Itâ€™s also weird to think that this old man would be compelled to attack obi wan if he saw that he was a jedi. I liked this detail that the empire is not taking care of the ckone soldiers. Like the channel heavy spoilers pointed out, the show the bad batch has shown us how the empire cast aside their clones becaus e aclone warmy was too expensive to maintain.|A dealer tries to sell him drugsâ€“I guess he has that look about him [wanna buy some death sticks?]. She mentions a spice called Kessel pureâ€“and Kessel is the planet where spice is mined, like we saw in Solo and the clone wars. And the other planet she names is Felucia, which we first saw here in Revenge of the Sith [planet where bellybutton jedi does it rots]. |And by the way that spice dealer is laid by esther rose mcgregor, the great niece of denis lawson, who played wedge antillesâ€¦and sheâ€™s also ewan mcgrgeoirâ€™s daughter,|This aurubesh sign reads Swartz, named after star wars producer jon swartz. |And on this station sign we see a navigational map of the galaxy that has popped up all over star wars. And there is a lot of aurbe sh here that is blurry anbd hard to read. But we were abkle to make out All travelers must be cleared|Kamail Nanjiani plays a con man with a heart of gold pretending to be a jedi, and he is great [clip]. He promises this family safe passage to Corellia, home planet of Han Solo we saw in Solo. And he claims this kid is force sensitive, but thatâ€™s obviously a con to get the family to shell out some cash.|And man, this guy got ripped to be in Marvel and Star wars, and they keep hiding that body under robes and stuff. Come on, the guy lived off egg whites for a year! Let him show off.|As Obi wan searches the square, he twirls his mustache. Alec Guiness did this in a new hope [when heâ€™s talking to luke in his house] and Ewan mcgregir later imitated this gesture at the d of revenge of the sith [dropping luke off]|When obi wan breaks into the space meth lab, he wears a mask that looks like Ralph maquarrieâ€™s original design for Luke. Thanks Grogu, not baby Yoda, for that observation. |The guy who hassles him in the hallway is a Zabrak, the same species as Dartgh maul. ASnd bill scurry on twitter points out that this one is a Faleen, like Prince Xizor from shadows of the empire.|Obi wan escapes from the authorities by getting them high, a trick that was pioneered by cheech and chong [clip, ]|During the fight, notice how punching people really hurts his hands. Even when Ben was fighting in the wars, he wouldn;t have been punching people much, so his soft little jedi hands wouldn't be used to the pain. |He enters Leiaâ€™s cell, much like Luke does in A New Hope, when his name drops ben [Iâ€™m here with ben kenobi]. And Kinzie L on twitter points out that the way he bends down is very similar to how her hologram spoke to him in a new hope. |#ObiWanKenobi #EasterEggs #StarWars

title: Will we get a Game 7? Heat-Celtics Game 6 Preview LIVE ğŸ€ | Hoop Streams
description: Welcome back to Hoop Streams live from Boston for Game 6 of the Eastern Conference Finals between the Boston Celtics and Miami Heat. title: COOK WITHIN MINS! Sesame Oil Chicken Noodles ä¸‰æ¯é¸¡ç‚’é¢ Chinese 3 Cup Chicken Chow Mein -Stir Fry Recipe
description: We used frozen chicken to cook this dish, so don't worry if you don't have access to fresh chicken. |We know how much you all enjoy chow mein or Chinese stir fried noodles, so we combined another of our favourite chicken stir fry recipe with stir fried noodles to make these 3 cup chicken chow mein. I'd also call this dish Sesame Oil Chicken Noodles because those are the exact ingredients we used in this recipe. Three cup chicken, known as ä¸‰æ¯é¸¡ (san bei ji) in Chinese, is a traditional Taiwanese dish. As this is a really versatile recipe, you can also use this three cup chicken recipe concept on mushrooms, squid, fish or tofu as well. Three cup chicken gets its name from the three cups of main ingredients used - sesame oil, Chinese cooking wine and soy sauce. The term cup actually refers to the proportion of the three ingredients, so if you use three tablespoons of sesame oil, use three tablespoons each of Chinese cooking wine and soy sauce. This dish is very simple to prepare. If you like sesame oil chicken and chow mein, you must try it. title: Israel deliberately killed Al Jazeera reporter Shireen Abu Aqla, Palestinian report says - BBC News

title: The Hidden Costs Of Amazon Shipping And Returns
description: Buying and returning on Amazon may seem extremely easy, but that simplicity comes at a cost.|Amazon has more than 115,000 drivers working under independent small businesses - Delivery Service Partners, or DSPs - who deliver Prime packages to doorsteps with one-day shipping. This is a large part of how Amazon delivers packages so quickly. CNBC talked to current and former Amazon DSP drivers about the pressures of the job. From urinating in bottles to running stop signs, routes that lead drivers to run across traffic, dog bites and cameras recording inside vans at all times - some of the 115,000 DSP drivers have voiced big concerns.|But once you receive your Amazon order, if there's any reason you are on happy, more than likely it can be returned. Sending back an online order has never been easier. Itâ€™s often free for the customer, with some retailers even allowing customers to keep the item while offering a full refund. Amazon returns can be dropped off at Kohlâ€™s, UPS or Whole Foods without boxing it up or even printing a label.|But thereâ€™s a darker side to the record number of returns flooding warehouses after the holidays.|â€œFrom all those returns, thereâ€™s now nearly 6 billion pounds of landfill waste generated a year and 16 million metric tons of carbon dioxide emissions as well,â€ said Tobin Moore, CEO of returns solution provider Optoro. â€œThatâ€™s the equivalent of the waste produced by 3.3 million Americans in a year.â€|Moore says online purchases are at least three times more likely to be returned than items bought in a store. In 2021, a record $761 billion of merchandise was returned, according to estimates in a new report from the National Retail Federation. That report says 10.3% of those returns were fraudulent. Meanwhile, Amazon third-party sellers told CNBC they end up throwing away about a third of returned items.|At the head of the pack, Amazon has received mounting criticism over the destruction of millions of items. Now the e-commerce giant says itâ€™s â€œworking toward a goal of zero product disposal.â€ Last year, it launched new programs to give sellers like Clausen new options to resell returns, or send them to be auctioned off on the liquidation market.|This record number of online returns has created a booming $644 billion liquidation market. As supply chain backlogs cause shortages of new goods and Gen Z shoppers demand more sustainable retail options, pain points for one sector of retail are big business for another.|The nation's only major public liquidator, Liquidity Services, resells unclaimed mail, items left at TSA checkpoints, and outdated military vehicles. It also refurbishes highly sought after electronics, from noise-canceling headphones to the machines that make microchips.|CNBC takes you on an exclusive tour inside a Liquidity Services returns warehouse outside Dallas, Texas, where unwanted goods from Amazon and Target are stacked to the ceiling before being resold on Liquidation.com or a variety of other marketplaces.|SEGMENTS:|00:00 Amazon DSP Drivers Reveal The Challenges Of One-Day Shipping (June 2021)|24:19 Where Online Returns Really End Up And What Amazon Is Doing About It (January 2022)|40:49 How Liquidating Unwanted Goods Became A $644 Billion Business (February 2022)|Â» Subscribe to CNBC: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBC|Â» Subscribe to CNBC TV: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCtelevision|Â» Subscribe to CNBC Classic: https://cnb.cx/SubscribeCNBCclassic|About CNBC: From 'Wall Street' to 'Main Street' to award winning original documentaries and Reality TV series, CNBC has you covered. title: 2022 Rivian R1T Unboxing | The Electric Truck Joins Our Long-Term Fleet | Price, Interior & More
description: The Rivian R1T is a fully electric pickup truck and is the latest vehicle to be added to the Edmunds' long-term fleet. In this video, join Ryan ZumMallen as he picks up our new 2022 Rivian R1T and takes a closer look at our new electric truck. Follow Ryan as he checks out all of the cool accessories (like a portable speaker and air compressor), takes a tour of the interior, and shows you all that goes into charging the R1T. We're a big fan of the Rivian electric truck, which won the Edmunds Top Rated Editors' Choice award, and we're excited to drive it for the next year. title: Floods, drought and the consequences of extreme weather | DW Documentary
description: Long periods of sunny weather; a few heavy rain showers. Thatâ€™s all fine...or is it? With increasing frequency, summer days are turning into long periods of drought, while rainfall is causing catastrophic flooding.|Whereas weather systems were relatively moderate and predictable in recent centuries, now they appear to have been thrown off balance. Whatâ€™s heading our way - and what can we do to protect ourselves?|29 May 2016 is a day Frank Harsch will never forget. The mayor was in his office at the town hall in Braunsbach near SchwÃ¤bisch Hall in southern Germany. The rain was coming down in buckets. Suddenly he felt the building vibrate. When he looked out of the window, he saw a wave of brown water crashing past, carrying cars and debris along with it.| |A storm and a few hours of heavy rain was all it took to transform a village stream into a devastating monster wave. Suddenly, Braunsbach was a disaster zone. Itâ€™s a situation thatâ€™s becoming all too familiar. The opposite scenario is equally common, of late: heatwaves and droughts that last several months. Despite the many flood catastrophes of summer 2021, in many regions itâ€™s simply too dry.|In other areas of Germany, trees are dying because moisture isnâ€™t penetrating deep enough into the ground to reach the roots. Rainfall has decreased to such an extent in recent years that forestry workers have been forced to come up with new ways to direct water to where itâ€™s most needed.|In the film, weather experts and climate researchers predict what the future may have in store for us. Their forecasts may be bleak, but there are solutions and initiatives in place to at least try and mitigate the effects of extreme weather events.|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: The TRUTH How I Broke My Shelby GT500 Wheel! Ready for Gumball 3000
description: We made it! It wasn't easy, but we're in Toronto with my Shelby GT500 for the start of Gumball 3000 2022. A couple of days ago, this was going to be mission impossible, but we're here and getting the full livery for the rally! New t-shirt: https://cheers.shmee150.com/listing/toronto-to-miami-2022?product=2|There's a lot to update; from originally planning to bring my AMG GT Black Series but the boat got held up, to seeing if we could try a factory Zenvo (mine is 1-2 months away), only for customs issues to make it impossible. However, given I own a ridiculously awesome American muscle car, it's a no brainer to drive it on this year's Gumball 3000, and hence drove up from New York City towards Toronto... until things went wrong.|Unfortunately, a mammoth pot hole caused some damage to at least one of the carbon fibre wheels equipped to my GT500 and rendered it unusable. Sourcing replacements has been no easy task and without the car community pulling together would have been impossible. However, Yonge Steeles Ford Lincoln Toronto made it possible to 'borrow' some wheels; @DrivewithRoy kindly drove a wheel all the way to New York State to the car, @Speedracer38 brought the tires and drove the car back to Toronto, my friend Jay picked us up to go to Montreal, @SaturnDrives helped with all the logistics in Canada, and Carbon Revolution have managed to source replacement wheels despite the stock issues in North America.|With the surreal situation of the car finally being ready to go, with no backup plan in place if it couldn't, we're straight over to the Gumball 3000 garage to see some of the other cars including an Aston Martin One-77 and McLaren P1, but also to install the full rally livery to my car, naturally, as team 150. |For this year's Toronto to Miami rally, we've launched our latest design t-shirt and hoodies which you can find right now: https://cheers.shmee150.com/listing/toronto-to-miami-2022?product=2|Thank you to everyone involved, especially @DrivewithRoy for going the extra mile to make sure this worked and we would get here!|https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCePeyaYCUsU8ifHtG54-j-Q|http://instagram.com/roy.cwl|Thanks for watching, Tim|Chapter:|00:00 Intro|01:01 What Happened?|08:08 Showroom Walkaround|11:44 On the way to Gumball!|14:43 Arriving at the Garage|15:26 Installing Gumball 3000 Stickers|20:15 UK Number Plates|23:52 More Stickers|24:35 My GT500 is Ready|25:31 Wrap Up|#Shelby #GT500 #Gumball3000||||Subscribe: http://bit.ly/Shmee150YT||Website: http://www.shmee150.com||Shop: http://shop.shmee150.com||Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/shmee150||Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/shmee150

title: The Bernard Purdie Interview: Steely Dan, Aretha Franklin & "The Purdie Shuffle"
description: Bernard Lee "Pretty" PurdieÂ (born June 11, 1941) is an AmericanÂ drummer, and an influential R&B, soul andÂ funkÂ musician. He is known for his precise musical time keeping and his signature use of triplets against a half-time backbeat: the "Purdie Shuffle." Purdie is known as a groove drummer with immaculate timing who makes use of precisionÂ half note, backbeats, and grooves. He often employs a straight eight groove sometimes fusing several influences such as swing, blues and funk. He created the now well-knownÂ drum patternÂ Purdie Half-Time ShuffleÂ that is aÂ bluesÂ shuffle variation with the addition of syncopatedÂ ghost notesÂ on the snare drum. Variations on thisÂ shuffleÂ can be heard on songs such asÂ Led Zeppelin's "Fool in the Rain" andÂ Toto's "Rosanna" (Rosanna shuffle). title: Uvalde parents were armed and ready to storm the school
description: Mario Jimenez spent two agonizing hours waiting outside Robb Elementary in Uvalde, Tex., before learning his son was safe. The fourth grader knew most of the victims killed in the May 24 mass shooting that claimed the lives of 19 children and two adults. Jimenez said he and other parents rushed to the school with their weapons to assist police. "I tried to go in and help them out.â€ Read more: https://wapo.st/3GnaROo. title: 'Not eager but...': Zelensky hints at talks with Putin to end war as Donbas assault intensifies
description: Ukraine president Volodymyr Zelensky said talks with Russian President Putin necessary to end the invasion however he added that Ukraine isnâ€™t eager to talk to Putin whose troops are invading the country. Zelensky slammed Russia for allegedly not being serious for peace talks with his government to end the conflict Ukraine president made these comments while addressing an Indonesian think tank. The Kremlin said on Friday that it blames Ukraine for the fact that peace talks between the two countries are frozen, saying it was unclear what Kyiv wanted. title: Luhut: Hampir 500 Ribu Hektare Kebun Sawit di Indonesia Tapi Kantor Pusatnya di Luar Negeri!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Pemerintah akan mengaudit perusahaan minyak kelapa sawit di Indonesia mulai Juni nanti.||||Hal ini disampaikan oleh Menteri Koordinator Bidang Kemaritiman dan Investasi, Luhut Binsar Pandjaitan saat Seminar Nasional di Sekolah Tinggi Teknologi Angkatan Laut, 25 Mei lalu.||||Luhut yang kini menjabat Koordinator dan Pengawas bersama Satgas Pangan terkait minyak goreng, menemukan ada 300 hingga 500 ribu hektare kebun sawit di Indonesia, dimana kantor pusat atau Head-Quarternya justru berada di luar negeri.||||Baca Juga Soal Penerapan Kembali DMO untuk Atasi Masalah Minyak Goreng, GIMNI Ragu Kebijakan Ini akan Sukses di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293121/soal-penerapan-kembali-dmo-untuk-atasi-masalah-minyak-goreng-gimni-ragu-kebijakan-ini-akan-sukses||||Sementara itu, gabungan pengusaha kelapa sawit Indonesia, GAPKI menyebut pengusaha di sektor kelapa sawit mengaku bisa tersenyum kembali karena saat larangan ekspor dicabut, maka perdagangan minyak kelapa sawit dan turunanya bergerak positif kembali.||||Audit perlu dilakukan untuk mengidentifikasi bisnis sawit di Indonesia.||||Mulai dari kebun sawit hingga kantor pusat dan alur pajaknya.||||Kebijakan teknis terkait audit perusahaan diyakini pemerintah akan mampu mengurai permasalahan minyak goreng yang telah berlangsung sejak awal tahun 2022.||||Pemerintah yakin dengan audit yang tepat, maka masalah stok dan penyaluran minyak goreng akan lebih efektif kedepannya.|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293258/luhut-hampir-500-ribu-hektare-kebun-sawit-di-indonesia-tapi-kantor-pusatnya-di-luar-negeri

title: India loses seven Army soldiers in Ladakh's Turtuk after their vehicle fell into Shyok River
description: Seven Indian Army soldiers lost their lives after the vehicle they were travelling in skidded off the road and fell in the Shyok river in the Turtuk sector of Ladakh on Friday. There were 26 soldiers in the vehicle, which was moving from the Transit Camp in Partapur to a forward location in sub-sector Hanif. The accident took place at 9 am around 25 km from Thoise. The vehicle fell to a depth of around 50-60 feet, resulting in injuries to all occupants. Watch this video for more.|#Army #IndianArmy #Ladakh #Shyok #India

title: Wagub Jawa Barat AJak Warga Mendoakan Keselamatan Eril Anak Ridwan Kamil yang Hilang di Swiss
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Pihak keluarga masih menantikan kabar baik terkait pencarian Emmeril Khan Mumtadz, putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil.||||Eril, dinyatakan hilang terseret arus Sungai Aare di Bern Swiss dan belum ditemukan.||||Menurut adik Ridwan Kamil, pencarian terhadap Eril sudah dilakukan selama 6 jam sejak dinyatakan hilang pada 26 Mei 2022 di Sungai Aare Bern Swiss.||||Pencarian tetap dilakukan dan hanya dihentikan ketika sore hingga malam.||||Tak lupa keluarga meminta dukungan doa untuk pencarian eril.||||Anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril, hilang, saat tengah berenang di Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss.||||Baca Juga Putra Sulung Ridwan Kamil Hilang, Keluarga: Eril Berenang dengan Adiknya, Ibu Atalia Tidak Ikut di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293192/putra-sulung-ridwan-kamil-hilang-keluarga-eril-berenang-dengan-adiknya-ibu-atalia-tidak-ikut||||Sebelum hanyut, Kamis 26 Mei, siang hari waktu Bern, Swiss, Eril berenang di Sungai Aare, bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Namun, saat ingin naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras.||||Kini Eril masih dalam pencarian tim SAR dan Polisi Swiss namun Eril belum juga ditemukan.||||Saat kejadian, ayah Emmeril, Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil berada di Inggris, bersama delegasi Pemprov Jawa Barat.||||Wakil Gubernur Jawa Barat meminta agar warga Jawa Barat turut serta mendoakan anak Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau biasa dipanggil Eril yang hilang di Bern, Swiss.||||Hingga kini Pemprov masih menunggu kabar terkait pencarian yang dilakukan di Bern Swiss.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293223/wagub-jawa-barat-ajak-warga-mendoakan-keselamatan-eril-anak-ridwan-kamil-yang-hilang-di-swiss

title: 2023 Nissan Z Review - Engine Swapped 370Z?
description: The 2023 Nissan Z packs a new engine and significant upgrades to an already solid platform.|Subscribe to Engineering Explained for more videos! - https://goo.gl/VZstk7|Recommended Books & Car Products - http://amzn.to/2BrekJm|EE Shirts! - http://bit.ly/2BHsiuo|The 2023 Nissan Z now features a 3.0L twin-turbo V6 engine producing 400 horsepower and 350 lb-ft of torque. It's paired to a 6-speed manual transmission (updated from the 370Z), or a new 9-speed automatic transmission. There's new electronic power assisted steering, replacing the previous gen's hydraulic steering, and a new clutch-type mechanical limited slip differential, replacing the old viscous limited slip differential. Mechanically, there are many similarities to the 370Z (same platform, though updated).|There are three available trims: Sport, Performance, and Proto. In my video I'm driving the Z Proto. The Performance package adds quite a bit: Rear Spoiler, Sport Muffler, Sport-Tuned Suspension, Limited Slip Differential, Sport Brakes, Larger Wheels/Tires, Rev-Matching (6MT), GT-R Paddle Shifters (9AT), Power Adjust Seats, Heated Seats, Leather Appointed Seats, 9.0â€ Nav Touchscreen, Bose Audio System, Aluminum Pedals, and HomeLink. Certainly worth the $10k price jump in my opinion. title: Presiden Jokowi Takziah Almarhum Buya Syafii Maarif, Yogyakarta, 27 Mei 2022
description: *Presiden Jokowi:  Buya Syafii Maarif Seorang Guru Bangsa*|Presiden Joko Widodo menyebut sosok Buya Syafii Maarif sebagai guru bangsa yang hidup dalam kesederhanaan. Demikian disampaikan Presiden Jokowi usai bertakziah dan menyampaikan belasungkawa secara langsung atas wafatnya almarhum di Masjid Gedhe Kauman, Yogyakarta, Jumat, 27 Mei 2022.|"Beliau adalah kader terbaik Muhammadiyah yang selalu menyuarakan tentang keberagaman dan selalu menyuarakan tentang toleransi umat beragama dan beliau juga selalu menyampaikan pentingnya Pancasila bagi perekat bangsa," ucap Presiden saat menyampaikan sambutan dalam prosesi penghormatan terakhir bagi almarhum.|Presiden Jokowi mengajak masyarakat Indonesia untuk mendoakan almarhum agar mendapat tempat terbaik di sisi Allah Swt.|"Kita semua adalah milik Allah dan hanya kepada-Nya lah kita akan kembali. Mari kita berdoa bersama semoga almarhum Buya Syafii Maarif diberikan tempat yang terbaik disisi-Nya dan diampuni segala dosa-dosanya, aamiin ya rabbal alamin," ujar Presiden.|Tiba di lokasi sekitar pukul 15.05 WIB, Presiden langsung menunaikan ibadah salat asar berjemaah. Setelahnya, Presiden melakukan salat jenazah berjemaah dengan imam Ketua Umum PP Muhammadiyah Haedar Nashir. Presiden Jokowi juga mengikuti prosesi penghormatan terakhir bagi almarhum.|Selanjutnya, Presiden Jokowi berpamitan dengan istri almarhum, kemudian turut mengantarkan jenazah keluar masjid menuju mobil jenazah. Setelahnya, Presiden bersama dengan rombongan menuju Pangkalan TNI AU Adi Sutjipto untuk kembali bertolak ke Jakarta.|Turut mendampingi Presiden saat bertakziah yaitu Menteri Sekretaris Negara Pratikno dan Gubernur Daerah Istimewa Yogyakarta Sri Sultan Hamengkubuwono X.|Yogyakarta, 27 Mei 2022|Biro Pers, Media, dan Informasi Sekretariat Presiden|Website: https://www.presidenri.go.id|YouTube: Sekretariat Presiden

With that out the way, thanks for clicking this, now let's get into Obi Wan Kenobi.|Ok so when we last saw Obi Wan we were watching him taking the moral and literal high ground as he got rid of his apprentice like Alan Sugar. The Jedi had fallen and Order 66 was now in full effect with the last remaining Jedi having to hideout in the bowels of the universe. After dropping Luke off at his Aunt and Uncles Obi Wan left on his Eiope who ends up popping up again. Jedi's hiding out after Order 66 and taking menial jobs is something that was a big focus in Fallen Order and in that we watched Kal Kestis hiding out whilst the Inquisitors searched for the rest of his kind. Inquisitors make a big entrance in these episodes and along with the new one Reva, we also have some of the classic ones like The Grand Inquisitor and Brother Five that we'll talk about in just a bit.|Now we open on the planet of Coruscant getting introduced to some of the younglings that end up getting drafted into this. We see the events of Order 66 play out first hand and this show really goes from 0-100 in the space of a couple of seconds. This is Jedi Velti who defends the children and it tells what I believe is the story of Reva. We learn that she is Third Sister a reckless Inquisitor that strikes first and asks questions later, but here she's just a scared kid.|Music - LAKEY INSPIRED - Arcade|SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/lakeyinspired|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lakeyinspired

title: The Case for a 4-Day Work Week | Juliet Schor | TED
description: The traditional approach to work needs a redesign, says economist Juliet Schor. She's leading four-day work week trials in countries like the US and Ireland, and the results so far have been overwhelmingly positive: from increased employer and customer satisfaction to revenue growth and lower turnover. Making the case for a four-day, 32-hour work week (with five days of pay), Schor explains how this model for the future of work could address major challenges like burnout and the climate crisis -- and shares how companies and governments could work together to make it a reality.|If you love watching TED Talks like this one, become a TED Member to support our mission of spreading ideas: http://ted.com/membership|Follow TED! |Twitter: http://twitter.com/TEDTalks|Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/ted|Facebook: http://facebook.com/TED|LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/ted-conferences|TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@tedtoks|The TED Talks channel features talks, performances and original series from the world's leading thinkers and doers. title: The woman 3D-printing schools in Madagascar â€“ BBC News
description: Maggie Grout has just printed her first school in Madagascar - only the second 3D-printed school in the world.|She started the NGO, Thinking Huts, as a teenager, with the aim of 3D-printing schools in countries where some children lack the opportunity to get an education.|Printing schools is fast, once the printer is set up, and saves on building materials.|Maggie says she is motivated to help underprivileged children partly because she was born in poverty in China, before being adopted by American parents.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Madagascar #BBCNews

title: Russia tightens grip on Ukraine's Donbas Region | DW News
description: Moscow has set it sights on gaining control of the Donbas, Ukraine's industrial heartland. Russian troops are attempting to encircle Ukrainian forces by seizing key highways in the region.|Ukraine says 50 towns in the region came under shelling Thursday, which killed at least 9 people. With Russian troops gaining ground, residents here see no escape in sight.|Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelenskyy is frustrated that the European Union has struggled to reach a consensus on its latest sanctions against Russia.|"How many more weeks will the European Union try to agree on a sixth package?" title: Elder David A. Bednar Answers Questions at The National Press Club
description: After his speech given at The National Press Club in Washington, D.C. on Thursday, May 26, 2022, Elder Bednar answered more than a dozen questions. Several of these questions and his answers are in this video including questions about the name of the Church, the growth of the Church in Africa, same-sex marriage, transgenders, Church finances, tithing and other topics.

title: Neena Gupta: I Want To Be In Every Scene of Panchayat 3 | Faisal Malik, Sanvikaa
description: Panchayat 2 actors Neena Gupta, Sanvikaa, Faisal Malik and Sunita Rajwar get together to celebrate the success of their web series. From Faisal Malik talking about Prahlad's emotional scene, Sanvikaa being hailed as the 'national crush' to the rivalry between Manju Devi and Kranti Devi, the actors spill all the beans. Panchayat cast also pick their favourite scene from Panchayat Season 2 and also share their expectation from the Panchayat Season 3. title: Isabela's bedroom (with something unexpected) ğŸŒ¸ Custom Encanto Lego build DIY
description: Do you think Lego will make more Encanto sets? Yeah, me too. But it will take them a while to get sets from inception to shop shelves, so in the meantime I'm going to make my own Madrigal family builds. Isabela's room was a no-brainer, but all that pink and flower-y stuff broke me after a while, it's just so much softness and pastel. And every surface covered with flowers. But I did my best to build a custom Isabela-perfect Encanto bedroom out of Lego, let me know what you think ğŸ˜˜|If you've just dropped by, I'm Ellie! Lego is an artistic medium and no matter your building expertise there is something here for everyone. Stick around and I'll build for you while I review new sets and create my own customs (MOCs). I tend to geek out about new pieces, get excited about learning new and interesting building techniques, giggle too much and just generally ramble. title: â€˜I use game-changer techâ€™: PM Modi's secret revealed at Indiaâ€™s biggest drone festival launch
description: PM Narendra Modi launched 150 remote pilot certificates at India's biggest Drone Festival - Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 in Delhiâ€™s Pragati Maidan. At the event, PM Modi detailed how technology and drones were helping him keep a track of development across India. He noted that the enthusiasm being seen in India regarding drone technology is amazing and said that this will emerge as a sector of employment generation in India. PM Modi interacted with kisan drone pilots and witnessed open-air drone demonstrations in the drone exhibition centre. Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 is a two-day event and is being held on May 27 and 28. title: 3D PEN vs POLYMER CLAY || Fantastic DIY Ideas You Need To See
description: Hi, everyone! ||Are you ready for new amazing and cool ideas and DIYs? Today we will show you how to make fantastic things with a 3D pen and polymer clay! Let's start with cool tutorial on how to make cute keyring for your backpack using epoxy resin and some polymer clay. It can also be a cool gift for your friend. Thanks to 3D pen, it is possible to make the cutest spoon to put food on your furry friend. We will also show you step-by-step tutorials on how to create nice hairpins and beautiful necklaces. You can mold small hot dogs or bright colorful lightning out of polymer clay and wear them as earrings. title: Russia Has â€œUpper Handâ€ In Donbas l Kyiv Accuses Putin Of â€œGenocideâ€ l Chechen Leader Warns Poland
description: Ukraine says the war in the east of the country has hit its fiercest level yet as Russian offensive intensifies in the region. The mayor of the city of Severodonetsk has said that at least 1,500 people have been killed in the region. Zelensky has accused Moscow of carrying out a "genocide" in the eastern region of Donbas. Zelensky has also urged the West to stop playing around with Russia and impose tougher sanctions on Moscow. US officials have reportedly said that the Biden administration is considering sending missile launchers to Kyiv. Chechen leader Ramzan Kadyrov has threatened to attack Poland in retaliation for its steadfast support to Ukraine. title: Chrishell Stause Wasn't Born In A Gas Station
description: Even though the internet likes to believe it's true, Chrishell Stause wasn't actually born in a gas station. Chrishell reveals her mom was at a Shell station when she went into labor, and a man named Chris called an ambulance for her and helped keep her calm. Her mom wanted to name her after the kind man, so she combine Chris with Shell and ended up with Chrishell. title: IAS couple dog walking row: Mahua, Omar question transfers to Arunachal, Ladakh | Internet in splits
description: A massive controversy has erupted in the national capital after a picture of an IAS couple walking their dog in Thyagraj Stadium went viral. Sanjeev Khirwar and Rinku Dugga, both 1994 batch officers of the AGMUT cadre, were forcing athletes to finish their training by 7 PM, so that they could bring their dog to the facility for daily evening walk. The Ministry of Home Affairs has now transferred the couple to Arunachal Pradesh and Ladakh. However, TMC MP Mahua Moitra and NC Leader Omar Abdullah have slammed this punishment posting claiming that it was demoralising to the people there to be given the impression that officers only get sent as a punishment. Meanwhile, the internet is in splits as the 2 officers have been sent to opposite ends of the country. Memes went viral asking who will take care of the dog amid all of this. Watch this video for more details.|#IASCouple #Dog #ThyagrajStadium #SanjeevKhirwar #RinkuDugga #ArunachalPradesh #Ladakh #Delhi #MHA #Centre #DelhiGovernment #ModiGovernment

title: 'Deceit in garb of ceasefire': Indian Army tears into Pak for pushing terror in Kashmir
description: Indian Army has hit out at Pakistan after three infiltrators were gunned near LoC in J&K's Kupwara yesterday. The Indian Army said that exporting terrorism in J&K has been a state policy of Pakistan for last three decades. Three heavily-armed terrorists from Pakistan were intercepted and killed by the forces in Kupwara. There has been a surge in infiltration attempts from Pakistan since the last many weeks along the LoC in J&K. The surge in terror infiltrations comes at a time when a ceasefire is in place on the border between India and Pakistan. Watch the full video for more.|#India #Pakistan #IndianArmy #LoC #Ceasefire #Terrorists #Terror #Kupwara #InfiltrationBid #JammuAndKashmir

title: SARWENDAH PENGEN MAKAN SOTO BETAWI, BETRAND AJAK JAJAN DI LUAR | The Onsu Family

title: Fakta-fakta Sungai Aare Swiss, Lokasi Hilangnya Emmeril Anak Sulung Ridwan Kamil
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Dikabarkan anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz (Eril), hilang terseret arus Sungai Aare, Bern, Swiss, Kamis (26/5/2022).||||Dalam keterangan resminya, adik Ridwan Kamil, Elpi Nazmuzaman menuturkan kejaidan berawal saat Eril berenang di Sungai Aare, Bern, bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Berikut sejumlah fakta mengenai Sungai Aare lokasi Emmeril terseret arus:||||Mengutip situs web Kota Bern, Jumat (27/5/2022), Sungai Aare bukan lokasi asing bagi warga lokal maupun turis.||||Baca Juga Kronologi Anak Ridwan Kamil Diduga Terseret Arus Saat Berenang di Sungai Aaree Swiss di https://www.kompas.tv/article/293083/kronologi-anak-ridwan-kamil-diduga-terseret-arus-saat-berenang-di-sungai-aaree-swiss||||Sungai Terpanjang di Swiss||||Dengan panjang 288 kilometer, Aare adalah sungai terpanjang yang mengalir sepenuhnya di Swiss bermuara di gletser Aar Bawah dan Atas di Bernese Oberland dan rutenya ke utara berakhir di Koblenz.||||Warisan Budaya Takbenda Swiss||||Sejak 2017, berenang di Sungai Aare merupakan tradisi dan karenanya masuk daftar warisan budaya tak benda UNESCO.||||Rekor Dunia Arung Jeram||||Rekor dunia untuk arung jeram Sungai Aare dibuat di Bern pada 2012, ketika total 1.268 orang secara bersamaan mengarungi sungai tersebut dengan perahu karet, dari Kiesen ke Eichholz.||||Lokasi Tradisi Zibeleschwmme||||Zibeleschwmme merupakan tradisi berenang di Sungai Aare saat musim dingin. Setelah berenang, mereka pun menghangatkan diri dengan suara karnaval "musik Guggen," teh panas, dan sup.||||Bagi Perenang Berpengalaman||||Berenang di Aare direkomendasikan hanya untuk perenang berpengalaman.||||Video Editor: Rengga||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/293087/fakta-fakta-sungai-aare-swiss-lokasi-hilangnya-emmeril-anak-sulung-ridwan-kamil
tags: anak sulung ridwan kamil|emmeril|emmeril hilang di swiss|sungai aare|sungai aare swiss|swiss

title: Schmitt Argues to Bailey That He Should Be Allowed to Donate Blood - Grey's Anatomy
description: Schmitt (Jake Borelli) argues that the rules that keep him from donating blood in the midst of a blood shortage are wrong, and Bailey (Chandra Wilson) agrees, but doesn't have a choice. Watch 'Grey's Anatomy' THURSDAYS 9/8c on ABC and Stream on Hulu.

title: Imran Khan heaps praise on India amid fuel price hike in Pak; Lauds Modi govtâ€™s strategy
description: Former Pakistan PM Imran Khan has once again praised India. Hitting out at the Shehbaz Sharif government for hiking fuel prices in Pakistan, Imran lauded India for being able to reduce fuel prices amid cheaper oil from Russia. In a series of tweets, Imran said the highest price hike is the price Pakistan will pay for the incompetent and insensitive government. "In contrast India, strategic ally of the U.S., has managed to reduce fuel prices by Pkr 25 per litre by buying cheaper oil from Russia. Now our nation will suffer another massive dose of inflation at the hands of this cabal of crooks." tweeted Imran. The Shehbaz Sharif government in Pakistan increased the prices of all petroleum products by Pak rupees (PKR) 30/litre to reduce fuel subsidies. The highest-ever increase in the prices of all petroleum products in one go is aimed at impressing the International Monetary Fund. Watch this video for more details.|#Pakistan #ImranKhan #FuelPrices #India #NarendraModiGovernment #ShehbazSharifGovernment #PKR #Petrol #Diesel #Petroleum

title: PM Modi inaugurates Bharat Drone Mahotsav at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi
description: Prime Minister Shri Narendra Modi will inaugurate India's biggest Drone Festival - Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 - on 27 May 2022 at 10 AM at Pragati Maidan, New Delhi.|Prime Minister will also interact with kisan drone pilots, witness open-air drone demonstrations and interact with startups in the drone exhibition centre.|Bharat Drone Mahotsav 2022 is a two day event and is being held on 27th and 28th May. Over 1600 delegates comprising government officials, foreign diplomats, armed forces, central armed police forces, PSUs, private companies and drone startups etc. will participate in the Mahotsav. More than 70 exhibitors will display various use cases of drones at the exhibition. Mahotsav will also witness a virtual award of drone pilot certificates, product launches, panel discussions, flying demonstrations, display of a Made in India Drone Taxi prototype, among others.|Subscribe Now: https://goo.gl/8qsb5E Stay Updated! ğŸ””||||Follow us to stay updated:||||â–º Download the NM App: http://nm4.in/dnldapp||â–º Like us on Facebook: https://facebook.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/narendramodi||â–º Follow us on Instagram: http://instagram.com/narendramodi|#BharatDroneMahotsav  #PragatiMaidan #NewDelhi

title: Anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz Hilang Teseret Arus Sungai di Swiss!
description: KOMPAS.TV - Anak sulung Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Khan Mumtadz atau biasa dipanggil Eril mengalami musibah di Bern, Swiss pada 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss.||||Musibah hilangnya anak sulung Ridwan Kamil tersebut terjadi saat Eril berenang di sungai Aaree, Bern bersama adik dan kawannya.||||Saat ingin naik ke permukaan, Eril terseret arus sungai yang cukup deras yang sebelumnya sempat mendapat bantuan dari kawannya.||||Kejadian tersebut terjadi pada tanggal 26 Mei 2022 siang hari waktu Swiss dengan kondisi cuaca cerah.||||Keluarga dari Ridwan Kamil sendiri saat itu sedang berada di Swiss untuk mencari sekolah untuk Eril yang akan melanjutkan ke jenjang S2.||||Saat kejadian, Pak Ridwan Kamil sedang berada di Inggris dalam kegiatan pemerintahan di luar negeri bersama delegasi dari Pemprov Jawa Barat. ||||----||||Jangan lewatkan streaming Kompas TV live 24 jam non stop di https://www.kompas.tv/live  agar kamu semua tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia.||||Subscribe juga channel YouTube Kompas TV  di https://www.youtube.com/c/kompastv dan aktifkan lonceng supaya kamu dapat notifikasi video terbaru langsung. ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/292998/anak-ridwan-kamil-emmeril-khan-mumtadz-hilang-teseret-arus-sungai-di-swiss

title: The Major Superhero Role Ray Liotta Regretted Turning Down
description: The late Ray Liotta had a remarkable on-screen presence, bring gravitas and intensity to a variety of roles, including mobster Henry Hill in "Goodfellas," the ghost of Shoeless Joe Jackson in "Field of Dreams," and a violent ex-convict in his 1986 breakout "Something Wild." Liotta also played several cops and detectives over the years, which is very interesting, considering he almost played "The World's Greatest Detective" back in 1989. Long before superhero movies were commonplace on the big screen, Liotta opted out of a role that would have changed his career forever. This is the major superhero role Ray Liotta regretted turning down.|#RayLiotta #Actor #Superhero|Read Full Article: https://www.looper.com/662589/the-major-superhero-role-ray-liotta-regrets-turning-down/

title: Indiana Jones 5: Harrison Ford Shares Tearful Moment With John Williams
description: Indiana Jones actor Harrison Ford shared a tearful moment with legendary composer John Williams onstage at Star Wars Celebration, where Ford congratulated his good friend on his recent 90th birthday. While on stage, Ford also shared a new still from Indiana Jones 5, the character's latest adventure directed by James Mangold. Ford shared very few details about the film other than it's almost finished, it premieres June 30, 2023 and Williams is providing his musical talents on the film.

title: Pak buckles under IMF pressure as Sharif govt hikes petrol and diesel prices by Rs 30
description: Cash strapped Pakistan increased the price of petroleum products by Rs 30 per litre. After the increase, the price of one litre petrol will be at Rs 179.85 and diesel at Rs 174.15 in Pakistan. Similarly, the kerosene in Pakistan now costs  Rs 155.95 per litre and light diesel at Rs 148.41. Pakistan finance minister Miftah Ismail made the announcement at a press conference last evening. The decision was announced a day after the talks between the pakistan govt & IMF failed to reach an agreement on an economic bailout and the IMF staff-level agreement for the revival of the usd 6 billion programme ended. Watch the full video for more.|#Pakistan #ShehbazSharif #Petrol #Diesel #IMF

title: Akshay Kumar praises J&K cop killed by Pak terrorists; 'Salutes' his father for son's sacrifice
description: Actor Akshay Kumar 'saluted' the father of J&K cop Mudasir Ahmad who died in a shootout with Pak terrorists. The cop was killed after he intercepted the terrorists in Baramulla district who resorted to firing. The policeman had retaliated and reportedly gunned down the three terrorists of Lashkar. His father later told the media that 'he was proud of his son's sacrifice he made for the sake of the country'. After the remarks of the cop's father went viral, Akshay Kumar showered praise on the duo. Watch the full video for more.|#AkshayKumar #MudasirAhmad #JammuAndKashmir #JammuAndKashmirPolice #India #Baramulla #Pakistan #Terrorists

title: Global National: May 26, 2022 | Police under scrutiny for response to Uvalde, Texas school shooting
description: As the overwhelming grief continues over the 19 children and two teachers killed in the Uvalde, Texas, school shooting, demands for answers are growing over how police responded to the massacre. Jackson Proskow looks at the timeline and the police actions outside the school that is drawing questions and confusion, as well as the harrowing account of one child who survived the attack.|And as Uvalde mourns those killed, several other children who survived the horrific tragedy are still fighting for their lives in hospital. Heather Yourex-West reports from San Antonio's University Hospital on how quick-thinking saved an 11-year-old, the physical and emotional scars young survivors like her will have to carry, and how the doctors helping them have learned from past tragedies.|In Canada, public health officers continue to watch out for more monkeypox infections as case numbers climb -- but giving out more information about them is proving to be controversial. Jamie Mauracher has more on the stigma surrounding the virus, the groups it affects, and how that creates challenges for tracking it.|With Ukraine cracking down on countless war crimes committed during Russia's invasion, investigators continue to find more gruesome evidence of atrocities inflicted on civilians. Jeff Semple speaks with residents in the war-torn city of Kharkiv, on the brutality dealt to their loved ones, as more war crimes are uncovered throughout the region.|In British Columbia, a year after the revelation of 215 unmarked graves near the former Kamloops Indian Residential School, the Tk'emlÃºps te SecwÃ©pemc First Nation is now moving forward with plans to identify and repatriate the remains. But as Neetu Garcha reports, the size and scope of the forensic work required could take years.|Canada's housing market was hot even before the COVID-19 pandemic hit, with prices leaving many wanting to purchase a home frustrated, but in the last few years that difficulty has soared as prices skyrocketed. In part three of Global News' "Sticker Shock" series, Anne Gaviola looks at the impact of housing inflation and how it's keeping many prospective buyers on the sidelines.|And widely known for his roles in 'Field of Dreams' and Martin Scorsese's mob movie classic 'Goodfellas,' 67-year-old Hollywood actor Ray Liotta has died in his sleep while shooting a movie in the Dominican Republic. Mike Drolet looks back at the stellar career in cinema Liotta has left behind.|For more info, please go to https://globalnews.ca/news/8873285/texas-school-shooting-question-police-response/|Subscribe to Global News Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/20fcXDc|Like Global News on Facebook HERE: http://bit.ly/255GMJQ|Follow Global News on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1Toz8mt|Follow Global News on Instagram HERE: https://bit.ly/2QZaZIB|#GlobalNews #TexasSchoolShooting #UvaldeTexas

title: Grief courses through Uvalde, Texas, as police response to the massacre is scrutinized
description: There were growing concerns Thursday about how police responded to the deadly elementary school massacre in Uvalde, Texas that left 21 people dead, 19 of them children. Police indicated the school doors may have been unlocked when the gunman entered and that he managed to stay inside for an hour before he was killed. The total prize fund is $150,000, with $750 for a win and $250 for a draw in the Prelims. The quarterfinals and semi-finals are 1-day, 4-game matches, while the final will feature two such matches over two days. The players have 15 minutes for all their moves, plus a 10-second increment starting from move 1. In the Prelims there are 3 points for a win and 1 for a draw. title: The Ending Of Top Gun: Maverick Explained
description: After 35 years of waiting, "Top Gun: Maverick" arrived in the summer movie season of 2022. It launched a new story in the saga of Pete "Maverick" Mitchell, the hotshot pilot from the original film who's older but not necessarily wiser, still flying planes as far and as fast as he can. An intriguing blend of old and new, "Top Gun: Maverick" is an attempt to recapture the spirit of the original film while also pushing things further and higher. While the ending doesn't have many big twists, there's still a lot of thematic importance that you might have missed. title: Russian forces tighten grip on eastern Donbas region | DW News
description: Russia is intensifying its campaign in Ukraine's eastern Donbas region, launching attacks on dozens of towns in Luhansk and Donetsk. The key industrial city of Severodonetsk is in growing danger of becoming completely surrounded. Having failed to capture the Ukrainian capital Kyiv and its second largest city Kharkiv, Moscow has focused on smaller objectives. |Ukrainian President Zelenskyy is demanding more heavy weaponry from the west â€“ describing the situation in Donbas as 'extremely difficult.'|German Chancellor Olaf Scholz has said that Russia's President Vladimir Putin cannot be allowed to win the war in Ukraine. |In an address to the World Economic Forum in Davos, Switzerland, Scholz repeated his country's support for Ukraine, but did not address Kyiv's demands for more heavy wepons. He said Russia's war is contributing to a global food crisis.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#WarInUkraine #Donbas #WEF

title: PM Modi on stage, Stalin re-ignites language war; Demands official language status for Tamil
description: Tamil Nadu Chief Minister MK Stalin on Thursday urged Prime Minister Narendra Modi to declare Tamil as the official language, like Hindi, at Union government offices and the Madras High Court. Stalin and Modi were sharing the stage at an event in Chennai, where the Prime Minister launched several new schemes and development projects.  PM Modi in return said that |'Tamil language is eternal and the Tamil culture is global'. Watch this video for more.|#India #Hindi #Tamil #NarendraModi #PMModi #TN #Chennai #HindiLanguageWar #HindiImposition #MKStalin #Stalin #DMK

title: How 'Everything Everywhere All At Once' Pulled Off Its Kung Fu Fight Scenes | Movies Insider
description: The fight scenes in "Everything Everywhere All at Once" put a fresh spin on classic kung fu movies. We spoke with stunt coordinator Timothy Eulich and fight choreographers Andy and Brian Le about how the movie's most impressive action sequences came together.|Timothy, Andy, and Brian worked with directing duo Daniel Kwan and Daniel Scheinert, aka the Daniels, to plan and execute the film's fight scenes on a tight budget and shooting schedule, shooting almost entirely within the confines of a single warehouse building in Southern California. Here, they talk about the inspirations and references they pulled from in choreographing the action in "Everything Everywhere," from classic Hong Kong movies and Jackie Chan action flicks to break dancing and parkour. |Timothy has worked as a stunt coordinator and performer on TV series like "Westworld" and "Stranger Things" and films like "Spider-Man: No Way Home" and "Cobra Kai." Previously, he collaborated with the Daniels on their A24-released "Swiss Army Man," starring Paul Dano and Daniel Radcliffe.|Andy and Brian are the brothers and self-taught martial artists behind the popular YouTube channel Martial Club. They appear in several scenes of "Everything Everywhere" as both actors and stunt doubles, most memorably opposite Michelle Yeoh in the IRS trophy fight. Previously, the siblings worked on Marvel's "Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings," with Andy playing the Death Dealer in the film.|"Everything Everywhere All At Once" is out in theaters.
